{"tid":2342534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強制檢測︱袁國勇爆3%高危群組交深喉唾液冇人類DNA 疑作弊呈水喉水","createTime":"2020-12-27T08:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T09:57:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c6039bd2d558cfbb0c1ed59a44a7d651c2432c","tid":2342534,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"政府要求多個高危群組強制檢測。政府專家顧問、港大微生物學系講座教援袁國勇在電視節目透露，發現過去1年約3%要接受檢測的高危群組，其樣本瓶未能測試到人類基因，「即係佢（測試）時畀啲水喉水我哋&hellip;&hellip;我哋攞返嚟應該測到人類DNA，但係無，證明有3%人未能誠實將深喉唾液交返嚟。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/353WEBFTBZFHBCP2O4IXIARBEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2F353WEBFTBZFHBCP2O4IXIARBEM%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e08a47ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2F353WEBFTBZFHBCP2O4IXIARBEM%2F&h=f5f68315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/353WEBFTBZFHBCP2O4IXIARBEM/</a>"},{"pid":"09d2a8650ea45687b0dcaf6dcdccba36e32302ac","tid":2342534,"uid":319380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"外星人侵略香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84164b2f0f91c159eec74e0552528019b735f675","tid":2342534,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c519c2d21d5ee3f241dabecfbfa55394ee120ea6","tid":2342534,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"828878f93efae4ae9fafaa61c4884484bd838a73","tid":2342534,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"中國人（含香港人）不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd6a1d3a8270a14427dde0630607d98b41a6dad","tid":2342534,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score